LOCATION:Virtual
SUMMARY:VIRTUAL EVENT: How to View Art!
DESCRIPTION:If you've always felt like you didn't know how to look at art
 \, you've come to the right place\; bring your lunch and hop on Zoom as w
 e show you a tried-and-true method for looking at things.  On the second 
 Monday of each month\, join Eskenazi Museum of Art's resident Arts-based 
 Wellness Experiences Manager Keaton Evans-Black to look at and talk about
  a piece of art from the IU museum collections using the see\, think\, wo
 nder framework.  No previous art experience necessary!
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  If you've always felt like you didn't k
 now how to look at art\, you've come to the right place\; bring your lunc
 h and hop on Zoom as we show you a tried-and-true method for looking at t
 hings.</p><p>  On the second Monday of each month\, join Eskenazi Museum 
 of Art's resident Arts-based Wellness Experiences Manager Keaton Evans-Bl
 ack to look at and talk about a piece of art from the IU museum collectio
 ns using the see\, think\, wonder framework.</p><p>  No previous art expe
 rience necessary!</p>
