LOCATION:INDIANA MEMORIAL UNION (UNION BUILDING)
GEO:39.167655;-86.523537
SUMMARY:Ryan White Memorial Sculpture Unveiling
DESCRIPTION:Date: Wednesday\, June 10\, 2026Time: 2:45ŌĆō4 p.m.Location: 
 Indiana Memorial Union (IMU)\, South LoungeFree and open to the public."K
 eep Going" was proposed by Provost Professor and RCAP Senior Director\, W
 illiam L. Yarber\, and was created by Melanie Cooper Pennington\, sculptu
 re area head and senior lecturer at the Indiana University School of Art\
 , Architecture + Design.Ryan was a Hoosier teenager renowned for his hero
 ic fight against the stigma of AIDS. He challenged misconceptions\, confr
 onted discrimination head-on\, and inspired people all over the world. He
  died from AIDS-related complications in 1990ŌĆöbefore he had the chance 
 to fulfill his dream of attending Indiana University. The bronze cast sta
 tue of Ryan will have a permanent home at the IMU\, where he will stand a
 mong students\, backpack and all.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><span data-contrast="auto"><strong>Date:<
 /strong> Wednesday\, June 10\, 2026<br /><strong>Time:</strong> 2:45ŌĆō4 
 p.m.<br /></span><strong>Location:</strong> Indiana Memorial Union (IMU)\
 , South Lounge<em><br /></em></p><p><em>Free and open to the public.</em>
 <span data-ccp-props="{}"></span></p><p><span data-contrast="auto">"Keep 
 Going" was proposed by Provost Professor and RCAP Senior Director\, Willi
 am L. Yarber\, and was created by Melanie Cooper Pennington\, sculpture a
 rea head and senior lecturer at the Indiana University School of Art\, Ar
 chitecture + Design.</span></p><p><span data-contrast="auto">Ryan was a H
 oosier teenager renowned for his heroic fight against the stigma of AIDS.
  He challenged misconceptions\, confronted discrimination head-on\, and i
 nspired people all over the world. He died from AIDS-related complication
 s in 1990ŌĆöbefore he had the chance to fulfill his dream of attending In
 diana University. The bronze cast statue of Ryan will have a permanent ho
 me at the IMU\, where he will stand among students\, backpack and all.</s
 pan><span data-ccp-props="{}"></span></p>
