 <p>  John Cheek has taught credit and non-credit classes for eight years 
 in portrait painting\, landscape painting\, palette knife painting\, life
  drawing\, beginning drawing\, and advanced drawing\, as well as in desig
 n. He volunteers his time and expertise to facilitate drawing workshops a
 t the Eskenazi Museum of Art.</p>
