DESCRIPTION:Through playful exploration and skill-building\, campers will
  learn how artists combine creativity and purpose\,transforming simple ma
 terials into beautiful\, useful works of art. By the end of the week\, ca
 mpers will take home a collection of unique creations that are both expre
 ssive and practical.  Art lessons and activities are thoughtfully designe
 d and led by our licensed art educator.  Drop-off and pick-up information
  will be shared via email after registration.12-3 pm Monday - Friday.
